There are so many places to Adventure in norrath no one camp should have such an impact on a Guild as to stop the beasts in Norrath ,Luclin or the planes from being Killed.<br>
This is what I propose:<br>
1) I will be sponsoring a 14 person raid on the Plane of Growth<br>
    a. raid will consist of one person from each of the 15   classes, (excluding BST)<br>
    b. Groups will be made and maintained by myself<br>
    c. PoG loot is mostly class specific Armor and Spells<br>
    d. Gem loot will be lotto at conclusion (thats the end)<br>
    e. Experience Will be Split evenly between groups.<br>
    f. I will Expect each Class to know there duties and will appreciate everyone respect towards each class.(ie don't be telling the shammy to slow or the cleric to heal)at the same time if you have any questions or are new to pog plz ask questions to avoid looking dumb or killing everyone.<br>
    g. Raid will be held Saturday March 9th from 10 am est to 8 pm est (plz include in your post available time so)<br>
    h. Raid will be open to first person to sign up from each class. If you are interested as alternate or replacement for a full class plz post anyway.<br>
    i. I realize 14 people is not even groups : 1 of the extras will be a none KOS ranger preferred. To assist in tracking and CR. This person will still get class related armor, spells and a nice chunk of the loot considering there Lack of EXp for the days effort. the other Extra will be the last class to sign up. They will still get armor and spells and cash loot. Their main duty will be Filling in for the first dropout. and any others things to be helpful.<br>
   j. To sign up contact me in game or post on the GENERAL boards<br>
2) Although PoG spits out killer loot and Exp I hope Everyone will learn something new and valuable about another class and possibly gain a new respect for All classes roles ingame.<br>
<br>
Yours on and off the Battlefield   Shylick  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bhordeofshadows15583.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=narina>Narina</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#8B0000>(2/27/02 7:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/fhordeofshadows15583frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=157.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Class Awareness/Appreaction</span><hr size=1> At first I thought you had an extremely good intent in your post/raid, but then I read this line...<br>
